        "adopterAction": "Port token cookie, header, TTL, SameSite, Secure, and HttpOnly policy into rest.CSRFConfig before enabling state-changing routes.",
        "rollbackOrEscalation": "Keep the previous CSRF layer when token issuance, validation, or browser cookie policy fails smoke coverage."
      },
